Honeymandias: Look Upon My Bees and Despair


10 Jun 2020 00:18






Well, here it is: my entry to the Exquisite Corpse Contest.

Like all good articles, the inspiration to this came to me while half asleep, and I quickly jotted  down so I wouldn't forget any of it. It was a puzzle to fit everything in the Containment Procedures, but I think I was able to make it work. A short, Ozymandias-style piece about failing to bring the past back.

My coauthor is Amelia Wright.

Image Source:  British bee journal (Public Domain)

Thanks to my reviewers:  Nameless Mediocre.

Thanks to Elogee for the name.








